{"tid":1032080,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Marvel隊長》破《神奇女俠》預售紀錄","createTime":"2019-02-22T06:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T12:37:42.000Z","uid":105567,"like":12,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba94b3e16226795e43c49801c036e85208337c8","tid":1032080,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:07:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190222/59289606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59289606&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=07239d03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190222%2F59289606&h=de75e64e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190222/59289606</a><br />\n<br />\nMarvel首部由女性超級英雄做主角的電影《Marvel隊長》（Captain Marvel），未上映先破售票紀錄。根據美國知名售票網Fandango統計，電影1月開始預售戲飛，累積至今不但緊貼《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers：Infinity War）和《黑豹》（Black Panther）登上Marvel預售票房榜第3位，更超越《神奇女俠》（Wonder Woman）和《水行俠》（Aquaman）上映前相同階段的預售表現，銷情非常理想。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有外媒估計由於《Marvel隊長》過去舉辦多場試映會都獲得正評，加上Marvel的宣傳策略，都大大提升預售票銷情，參照《神奇女俠》的表現，推斷《Marvel隊長》開畫首個周末的票房可達逾億美金。"},{"pid":"163ff2718797ada98379ae06493d3776dbf06a16","tid":1032080,"uid":84275,"like":13,"dislike":13,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:43:15.000Z","msg":"又贏DC狗一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fb535e4bca4367e1837e7fbe4014d45c558e7b","tid":1032080,"uid":221198,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"經期隊長"},{"pid":"d990a7a23d951a783e1e497119f6207bbb3b1a23","tid":1032080,"uid":103230,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔係咁踩套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎呢度同出面係平衡世界"},{"pid":"f20f0e2